scenes.description: The stage screen displays the logo and name of the live performance, "Selfish of a Rough Stone," with intro music playing.
Hoshimachi Suisei performs her song "TEMPLATE" on stage with backup dancers.
Hoshimachi Suisei makes several announcements regarding her new single and 4th-anniversary commemorative goods.

subtitles.original: 画面の向こうのそのまた向こうで
subtitles.english: Beyond the screen, and even further beyond that,

subtitles.original: 放たれた言葉たち
subtitles.english: the words that have been unleashed.

subtitles.original: 殴っても痛まない透明な拳
subtitles.english: Transparent fists that don't hurt even when they strike.

subtitles.original: 満天の星のように散らばっている
subtitles.english: Scattered like a sky full of stars,

subtitles.original: ガラスの破片の上を
subtitles.english: above the shards of glass,

subtitles.original: 裸足で歩くような痛みだ
subtitles.english: it's a pain like walking barefoot.

subtitles.original: 僕はずっと苦しかったんだ
subtitles.english: I've been suffering all this time.

subtitles.original: さあ僕にとって正解なんてどうだっていい
subtitles.english: Now, for me, I don't care what the "correct answer" is.

subtitles.original: 「正解」なんてどうだっていい
subtitles.english: "Correct answer" doesn't matter.

subtitles.original: この生が正しいか間違いか自分で決めるから
subtitles.english: Whether this life is right or wrong, I'll decide for myself.

subtitles.original: その手に抱えた
subtitles.english: In your hands,

subtitles.original: 大層なテンプレート 打ち砕いて
subtitles.english: smash that grand template you hold.

subtitles.original: 鏡に映った僕の色は全部
subtitles.english: All the colors of me reflected in the mirror

subtitles.original: 僕のためにあったのに
subtitles.english: were supposed to be for me.

subtitles.original: 気づいたらこの手を離れていた
subtitles.english: But before I knew it, they'd left my hands.

subtitles.original: 名前も顔も隠したアノニマスに
subtitles.english: To an Anonymous who's hidden both name and face,

subtitles.original: 僕の何がわかるの？
subtitles.english: what do you know about me?

subtitles.original: 輪郭さえぼやけそうな痛みも
subtitles.english: Even the pain that makes my silhouette blur,

subtitles.original: 僕の全部、取り返さなくちゃ
subtitles.english: I have to take it all back, everything that's mine.

subtitles.original: 何度遮ったってうるさいほどに鳴るノイズが
subtitles.english: No matter how many times I block it out, the noise that rings out so loud it's annoying,

subtitles.original: 好き放題僕をカテゴリーの檻に縛っても
subtitles.english: even if it binds me in a cage of categories as it pleases,

subtitles.original: この声の正体
subtitles.english: the true identity of this voice...

subtitles.original: 名前をつけるのは自分だけだろう？
subtitles.english: I'm the only one who can name it, right?

subtitles.original: もう僕は祈らない
subtitles.english: I won't pray anymore.

subtitles.original: この街の頭上を
subtitles.english: Above the head of this city,

subtitles.original: 降り注いだ慈愛を仰ぎはしない
subtitles.english: I won't look up at the pouring affection.

subtitles.original: 僕のこの痛みも姿形も
subtitles.english: My pain, my appearance, my form,

subtitles.original: 誰に決められることもない
subtitles.english: no one can decide those for me.

subtitles.original: さあ僕にとって正解なんてどうだっていい
subtitles.english: Now, for me, I don't care what the "correct answer" is.

subtitles.original: 「正解」なんてどうだっていい
subtitles.english: "Correct answer" doesn't matter.

subtitles.original: この生が正しいか間違いか自分で決めるから
subtitles.english: Whether this life is right or wrong, I'll decide for myself.

subtitles.original: あの一等星の輝きにも
subtitles.english: Even in the radiance of that first-magnitude star,

subtitles.original: 幸福が蔓延る理想郷にも
subtitles.english: even in a utopia where happiness flourishes,

subtitles.original: 届かなくたって構わない
subtitles.english: I don't mind if I don't reach them.

subtitles.original: 僕以外、何も要らない
subtitles.english: I don't need anything but myself.

subtitles.original: 星街すいせいニューシングル「TEMPLATE」
subtitles.english: Hoshimachi Suisei's new single, "TEMPLATE".

subtitles.original: 「天球、彗星は夜を跨いで」を手掛けたキタニタツヤさんに書き下ろしてもらいました！
subtitles.english: It was written by Tatsuya Kitani, who also worked on "Tenkyu, Suisei wa Yoru wo Mataide"!

subtitles.original: この後24時から各音楽配信サービスにて配信開始となります！
subtitles.english: Distribution will start on various music streaming services from midnight tonight!

subtitles.original: 先ほど披露したカリオペとのデュエット曲「Wicked」もカップリング曲として一緒に配信されますよ！
subtitles.english: The duet "Wicked" with Calliope, which we just performed, will also be released together as a coupling track!

subtitles.original: そしてこの後「TEMPLATE」のMVがすいせいチャンネルで投稿されるので、ぜひ見てください！
subtitles.english: And the music video for "TEMPLATE" will be posted on the Suisei Channel right after this, so please check it out!

subtitles.original: そして！
subtitles.english: And!

subtitles.original: なんと「TEMPLATE」が「太鼓の達人プラス」にて最速無料配信されます！
subtitles.english: Believe it or not, "TEMPLATE" will be available for free on "Taiko no Tatsujin Plus" starting immediately!

subtitles.original: 3月31日の22時から「Prism Melody」と同時配信となりますので、皆さんぜひ遊んでみてください！
subtitles.english: It will be released simultaneously with "Prism Melody" from 22:00 on March 31st, so please give it a try!

subtitles.original: さらに、誕生日と活動4周年を記念した記念グッズの発売も決定しました！
subtitles.english: Furthermore, we've decided to release commemorative goods to celebrate my birthday and 4th anniversary!

subtitles.original: グッズはアクリルパネル、キャップ、サーモタンブラー、スマホリングの4種類となっています！
subtitles.english: The goods consist of four types: acrylic panel, cap, thermo tumbler, and smartphone ring!

subtitles.original: この4つがセットになった「フルセット」もございます！
subtitles.english: There's also a "Full Set" containing all four items!

subtitles.original: フルセットには箔押しサイン入りのポストカードが付いてくる豪華仕様です！
subtitles.english: The full set is a luxurious version that comes with a foil-stamped signed postcard!

subtitles.original: この後22時から販売開始となりますので、チェックよろしくお願いします！
subtitles.english: Sales start at 22:00 after this, so please check it out!
